designerReference._value: You are required to enter a new Password. Make sure this banking password is completely unique and not used for any of your other apps, email or website logins.

<input required [pattern]="page.passwordPattern" formControlName="old" type="password" style="width: 98%; height:100% ; border: 2px solid gray;
    border-radius: 20px; font-size: 20px; padding-left: 10px;">

<input [pattern]="page.passwordPattern" required formControlName="password" type="password" style="width: 98%; height:100% ; border: 2px solid gray;
    border-radius: 20px; font-size: 20px; padding-left: 10px;">

<input [pattern]="page.passwordPattern" required formControlName="confirmPassword" type="password" style="width: 98%; height:100% ; border: 2px solid gray;
    border-radius: 20px; font-size: 20px; padding-left: 10px;">
Your password must be between 7 and 30 characters long.

Your Password must contain at least 3 of the following character types:
  • Lower case (a - z)
  • Upper case (A - Z)
  • Numbers (0 - 9)
  • Special characters (!@#$%&...)
Passwords may not be the same as your username.
